boxOfficeInfo.phoneNumberDetail: Olympia Box Office enquiries: (+353) 1 679 3323. To speak to a representative for information only, no bookings can be taken over the phone. Ticketmaster Booking Line for The Olympia: 0818 719 330 from Republic Of Ireland, for the UK and NI please call 0844 847 2455. Special Needs Booking Line:(+353) 1 516 9056.
boxOfficeInfo.openHoursDetail: Opening times are subject to performance schedule, however generally the box office is open from 10.30am to 6.30pm from Monday to Saturday. If there is a show on that evening it is opened until shortly after the show has commenced. If there is an event on a Sunday, the box office will be open 2 hours before the show starts, until shortly after the show has commenced.
boxOfficeInfo.acceptedPaymentDetail: Cash / Cheque / Visa / Mastercard / American Express / Laser
boxOfficeInfo.willCallDetail: While this can vary depending on the event, generally you can collect tickets in advance, or else on the day before the show. Bring the card the tickets were booked under, and the Ticketmaster reference number. If there are stricter rules for particular shows (for example, only the cardholder can gain entry with card, ID etc), this will be outlined upon booking.

venues.parkingDetail: Nearest available car parks are Jurys Inn Christchurch, Trinity St Car Park, Fleet St Car Park & Drury Street Underground Car Park.
venues.accessibleSeatingDetail: The staff at The Olympia Theatre will look after any dedicated special needs queries you might have, you can call them on our Special Needs Booking Line (+353) 1 516 9056, or email specialneeds@olympia.ie. If you have a special accommodation request (e.g. wheelchair seating, medical needs, hearing or sighting impairment) please feel free to discuss with us and our staff will do everything we can to help.
